{"id":107638,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/牛刀：9月房价上涨是因为8月货币的滥发/","date":"2010-09-25T02:21:10Z","modified":"2010-09-25T02:21:10Z","title":"牛刀：9月房价上涨是因为8月货币的滥发","content":"<p><p><span>牛刀：<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月房价上涨是因为<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>月货币的滥发<span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月上旬，全国各大城市房价一反常态，开始上涨。很多人开始发问，为什么在宏观调控的背景下，房价开始上涨，是假性回暖还是真实上涨，今天终于有了答案，那就是，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月房价开始的是真实上涨，绝不是假性回暖。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n为什么？我们来看看今天刚刚发布的数据：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月末，广义货币</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(M2)</span><span>余额</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">68.75</span><span>万亿元，同比增长</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19.2%</span><span>，增幅比上月高</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.6</span><span>个百分点，比去年同期低</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9.3</span><span>个百分点；狭义货币</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(M1)</span><span>余额</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24.43</span><span>万亿元，同比增长</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21.9%</span><span>，增幅比上月和去年同期分别低</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.0</span><span>和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5.8</span><span>个百分点；流通中货币</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(M0)</span><span>余额</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3.99</span><span>万亿元，同比增长</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16.0%</span><span>。当月净投放现金</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">380</span><span>亿元，同比多投放</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">213</span><span>亿元。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n看看这个数据，我们就找到了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月房价上涨的理由。那就是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月份的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">M2</span><span>比</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月份增幅高出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.6%</span><span>，也就是说，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月货币投放比</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月份多出了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span><span>亿左右。按涉房地产比重计算，这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1000</span><span>亿的贷款至少有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>多亿增幅的资金流进房地产，推动了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月房价的上涨。要知道去年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月正是货币增长最快的月份。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span><br />\n同时从央行的基础货币投放也可以看出，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月份净投放现金</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">380</span><span>亿，比去年同期多投放</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">213</span><span>亿。去年，是中国人民银行投放货币最多的年份，而今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月居然比去年还要高出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60%</span><span>，房价焉能不涨？调控还有什么意义？</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span><span><br />\n牛刀淘宝书屋重新开张<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span></span>另有曹建海亲笔签名新书《向高房价宣战》和王福重签名新书《写给中国人的经济学》：网址<span lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://shop58544884.taobao.com/\"><span><span>http://shop58544884.taobao.com</span><span>/</span></span></a></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[9203],"tags":[]}